### Key design decisions
- **`msg.value("role", "")` / `msg.value("content", "")`** — matches the pattern used by every other handler
- **System merged into first user turn only**, separated by `\n`
- **`tmpl.bos_token()`** provides `<s>` — model-agnostic, consistent with how the template object is used elsewhere
- **`COMMON_CHAT_FORMAT_CONTENT_ONLY`** — the default format value; no PEG parser/grammar needed since this is a simple fixed format
- **Detection excludes `[SYSTEM_PROMPT]`** as a guard — the Ministral 3 check fires first anyway (it checks `[SYSTEM_PROMPT]`), so there's zero routing conflict
